      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Mesh convergence and discretization error assessment",
      "description": "Grid convergence index (GCI) computed for three mesh refinement levels using Richardson extrapolation. GCI for pressure head QoI is 1.7%, within acceptable bounds for MRL 2.",
