      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution plausibility check",
      "description": "Wall shear stress distributions compared qualitatively against published literature for similar centrifugal pump geometries. High-shear regions identified near blade leading edges are consistent with expected hemolysis hotspots. Variability attributable to manufacturing tolerances and blood rheology variation across donors is discussed in prose within the validation report but no UQ artifact is attached."
    }
