    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device. RH < 1 criterion satisfied at all operating points. The assessment team notes that aleatory uncertainty from blood donor variability and in vitro assay repeatability is acknowledged qualitatively in the validation report narrative; formal UQ artifact linkage for all validation results is recommended for future MRL 3 assessments but is not required at the current risk level.",
